column1: These are the thorax length bristle number and wing length data from the Drosophila selection experiment published in:
Scheiner SM Caplan RL and Lyman RF. 1991. The genetics of phenotypic plasticity. III. Genetic correlations and fluctuating asymmetries. Journal of Evolutionary Biology 4:51-68.
See Materials and Methods section for details.
